Public Functions

cssioDecomp 
 int cssioDecomp(void *data_in,
                 int data_in_len,
                 void *data_out,
                 int npts,
                 const char *datatype,
                 int outtype)
Decompress a waveform.

Parameters:
data_in - The compressed data.
data_in_len - The number of bytes in the data_in array.
data_out - An integer or float array of length npts to receive the data values.
npts - The number of data values to return.
datatype - The data compression type. ("s4", t4", s2", "g2", "s3", "i4", "f4", "c2", "c4", or "ca")
outtype - The desired data type of the output values (FLOAT_DATA or INT_DATA).
